會輸，唔好再俾膠post分散我地嘅注意力，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">同我推晒下面啲post上熱門！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">催淚彈、胡椒噴霧</span></span><br />\n發夢夢到幾個德國朋友教我點處理催淚彈 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1218344/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1218344/page/1</a><br />\n[Gear撚] 催淚彈對防指南 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1214624/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1214624/page/1</a><br />\n［學術］中咗催淚彈同胡椒噴霧解決方法 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1223200/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1223200/page/1</a><br />\n[廣傳][長文]長期革命，每個人都要準備對抗催淚彈/胡椒噴磅必須用品 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1217785/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1217785/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">裝備</span></span><br />\n&lt;抗爭手冊&gt; <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1085603/page/2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1085603/page/2</a><br />\n振興香港消費！全城戶外運動裝備及須知 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1224572/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1224572/page/1</a><br />\n知己知彼 百戰百勝圖解香港警察裝備 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1206461/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1206461/page/1</a><br />\n最近有個新喪屍GAME IDEA <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1222684/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1222684/page/1</a><br />\n[突發] 621 雙方陣營裝備分析 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1240449/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1240449/page/1</a><br />\n[魔防的重要性］所有人都要有足夠魔防 N95同泳鏡係最低要求 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1242265/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1242265/page/1</a><br />\n星期五嘅野餐行動 請現在立即做兩樣野 購買裝備 同 加強文宣 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1241812/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1241812/page/1</a><br />\n[突發]新假期繼野餐之後又癡咗線 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1242741/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1242741/page/1</a><br />\n緊急！邊度可以買魔防裝 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1242751/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1242751/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">盾牌</span></span><br />\n[歷史台][積極備盾] 盾牌陣不是亂擺一通的 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1241049/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1241049/page/1</a><br />\n廉價盾牌材料 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1200677/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1200677/page/1</a><br />\n對付警犬最強盾牌buff <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1216654/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1216654/page/1</a><br />\n得黑警有盾牌？我都有！ <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1225742/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1225742/page/1</a><br />\n盾牌警棍頭盔：反政府示威者裝備不輸警察 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1240310/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1240310/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">物資</span></span><br />\n作為一個物資站站長，我想同大家道個歉 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1222678/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1222678/page/1</a><br />\n野餐物資／通訊檢討小組（重開）<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1217849/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1217849/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">鐵馬</span></span><br />\n鐵馬一定要放最前！鐵馬一定要有流動性！ <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1238720/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1238720/page/1</a><br />\n[人人都要識] 倒三角扎鐵馬 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1240447/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1240447/page/1</a><br />\n鐵馬最新安置法 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1216269/page/1?post=2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1216269/page/1?post=2</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">地形</span></span><br />\n圖解香港禮賓府旅遊路線 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1241712/page/2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1241712/page/2</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">IT</span></span><br />\n[正式上架] 手機抗警犬 用相機Scan數字即出黑警資料 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1241300/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1241300/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"ccf7e9034e739e6957df97aedbc3343e98efced7","tid":1240310,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfdf44071890ce797495914edcd4b42060c2cf89","tid":1240310,"uid":184679,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:09:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img1.gtimg.com/8/859/85971/8597142_980x1200_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gtimg.com%2F8%2F859%2F85971%2F8597142_980x1200_0.jpg&h=37d86211&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:51:55.000Z","msg":"聖戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9faab48774bd8b72bdda6c86f63c091c46a2f119","tid":1240310,"uid":161626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:02:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5a195d2946602107d51e7c6630dda48a4a3fcf35","tid":1240310,"uid":70201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:04:41.000Z","msg":"[香港加油] 想喺聽日deadline前激勵下大家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1243430\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1243430</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"16f40feab24b6812f6734988170b9bc81305a457","tid":1240310,"uid":161626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:21:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"51d51d9b66462edde3b9d840